comments: Richardson (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Gordon (ORL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Gordon (ORL) makes contact to the body of Wade (MIA) during the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Vucevic (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Waiters (MIA) and does not deliver contact.
Adebayo (MIA) makes contact to the body of Vucevic (ORL) during the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Adebayo (MIA) delivers leg to leg contact to Gordon (ORL) during the screen, causing Gordon to lose his balance and make contact with Wade (MIA) that affects his SQBR.
Augustin (ORL) places a hand/arm to the front of Dragic (MIA) during the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Gordon (ORL) places a hand/arm to the front of Wade (MIA) during the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Adebayo (MIA) and Vucevic (ORL) engage and disengage during the rebound.
Augustin (ORL) maintains his pivot foot.
Vucevic (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Dragic (MIA) and does not deliver contact.
Wade (MIA) makes contact to the body of Gordon (ORL) at the start of the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Richardson (MIA) places a hand/arm to the front of Ross (ORL) at the start of the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Richardson (MIA) makes contact to the arm of Ross (ORL) during his shooting motion that affects his jump shot attempt.
Augustin (ORL) places a hand/arm to the front of Dragic (MIA) during the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Olynyk (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Fournier (ORL) and gives him room to avoid the screen.
Waiters (MIA) commits a take foul on Augustin (ORL).
Fournier (ORL) makes marginal contact to the body of Waiters (MIA) during his shooting motion that does not affect his play at the basket.
Olynyk (MIA) commits a take foul on Gordon (ORL). When the contact occurs the ball is still below the tip of the circle in the backcourt, resulting in a common foul.
During the rebound, Richardson (MIA) briefly grabs the jersey of Carter-Williams (ORL) but does not affect his ability to secure the rebound.
Olynyk (MIA) makes marginal contact with Augustin (ORL).
[Observable in enhanced video] Augustin (ORL) lifts his pivot foot prior to the release of his dribble.
Waiters (MIA) commits a take foul on Augustin (ORL).
Fournier (ORL) makes incidental contact to the arm of Waiters (MIA) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Dragic (MIA) commits a take foul on Augustin (ORL).
Carter-Williams (ORL) places a hand/arm to the front of Waiters (MIA) during the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Isaac (ORL) and Olynyk (MIA) engage and disengage during the rebound.
Dragic (MIA) commits a take foul on Carter-Williams (ORL).
